::Kluster/Prowl::

Kluster narrows his eyes, looking at Koj. "I don't know about how 
Maximals worked in the past since I only got here recently, but I'm 
not aware that stealing is regular procedure. You could have asked 
for the supplies, and they would have probably been provided. 
Stealing, though, is not a way to solve anything."

He looks at Klant, frowning. "What do you mean? I wasn't aware of 
tortured prisoners. Mean bots are on all factions, though.."

Kluster pushes the comm button again. "All Maximals, we're about to 
start. Anyone who's not here yet, get here."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl frowns as he recieves Kluster's transmission.

-Love, if we're planning to be in the meeting, we need to get there 
soon.-
